    "Assume that each news in the training data of this paper is multimodal news (containing images and text), In this setup, D s { p i, y i } represents historical news (source event).",
    "p i (t i, v i), where t i represents the textual information of the news, and v i represents the image information of the news.",
    "y i (y i, d i) is the labeling of the news, d i is the domain labeling of the news, and y i is the true/false labeling of the news.",
    "The emergent event (target event) is D T ( p i).",
    "Based on the difficulty of less labeled and multimodal news in the social media fake news detection task described in the previous section, this paper simulates this difficulty in data partitioning."
